com.atakmap.android.missionpackage.ui

Class MissionPackageListGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atakmap.android.missionpackage.ui.MissionPackageListGroup

  • public class MissionPackageListGroup
extends java.lang.Object
    Container for managing a Mission Package in the ATAK UI. Tracks user changes against baseline (what is currently in the .zip on SD card). Also keeps a list of UI elements representing each item in the Mission Package contents
